# ===================== PART 4 (Week 6 Slides) =====================

### USERS – Register (slides route)
# Use a BRAND-NEW email each time to avoid "Email already in use".
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/users
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Admin",
  "email": "admin9@example.com",
  "password": "Passw0rd!"
}
###
# Copy the returned "_id" and paste into @userId at the top.

### AUTH – Sign in (slides)
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/signin
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "admin9@example.com",
  "password": "Passw0rd!"
}
###
# Copy the "token" (NO quotes) and paste into @token_v6 at the top.

### USERS – Read (PROTECTED with Bearer token)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/users/{{userId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token_v6}}
###

### USERS – Read (NO TOKEN → should be 401)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/users/{{userId}}
###

### AUTH – Sign out (slides)
GET {{baseUrl}}/auth/signout
###
